DOC.brief_summary: The purpose of this study is to evaluate long-term outcome of treatment(percutaneous coronary intervention or coronary-artery bypass graft) in unprotected left main coronary artery stenosis in Korea.
DOC.brief_title: Ten-Year Outcomes of Stents Versus Coronary-Artery Bypass Grafting for Left Main Coronary Artery Disease
DOC.criteria: Unprotected left main disease Exclusion Criteria : No exclusion criteria
